content: but i think the Verizon outage is keeping me from getting the Zoom link.  Can it be posted here?
Hi <@1170136212279918633> !  Our new Dials from Dawn to Dusk program started today.  You do not have to get into Zoom with this program.  https://events.democrats.org/event/704955/
When you click the link, enter your information, and then you'll get immediately directed to the dialer!
There is more information (including the debrief form) in the <#1242256751445934262> channel under the thumbtack (Pinned Messages).  Let us know if there is anything that you need help with!
Thank you so much!  I'll just hang onto this.  I hope i get my phone service back soon!
